    <briefdescription>
<para>classe <ref refid="classViscosite__turbulente__WALE" kindref="compound">Viscosite_turbulente_WALE</ref> </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>                                         (Sij_d * Sij_d)^1.5
</verbatim> visc_SGS = (Cw * delta)^2 * ------------------------------------------------<mdash/>, (Sij_bar * Sij_bar)^2.5 + (Sij_d * Sij_d)^1.25</para>
<para>avec <verbatim>Sij_d = 0.5 * (gij_bar^2 + gji_bar^2) -1/3 gkk_bar^2,
gij_bar = du_i / dx_j,
gij_bar^2 = gik_bar * gkj_bar,
Sij_bar = 0.5 * (du_i / dx_j + du_j / dx_i)
